{"tid":1426995,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"【拋磚】九月公共教室/自修室","createTime":"2019-08-07T04:36:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T09:23:40.000Z","uid":70217,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d3d1771e481573d9c1c5c42fd8474b6a2b5e9b3a","tid":1426995,"uid":70217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T04:36:16.000Z","msg":"代冇ac文藝界朋友post: <br />\n<br />\n是咁的，九月就快嚟，好多學生都要返學<br />\n有冇可能將抗爭融入生活<br />\n等小朋友可以發表意見之餘<br />\n又唔會俾位人入佢地荒廢學業？<br />\n<br />\n以下為個人建議：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">非佔領</span></span><br />\n時間為<span style=\"color: blue;\">放學後到晚上</span><br />\n受眾教育程度以<span style=\"color: violet;\">初中至學士</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔洗着校服</span></span><br />\n邀請一啲義教/學者搞<span style=\"color: gold;\">研討會/補習班</span><br />\n學生亦都可以自行<span style=\"color: gold;\">聚集自修</span><br />\n公眾人士可以加入陪讀<br />\n但注意<span style=\"color: orange;\">學生：陪讀比例為1:&lt;=2</span><br />\n一方面可以照顧到小朋友嘅學業<br />\n另一方面可以做到公眾教育<br />\n例如啲維園亞伯冇嘢做可以嚟聽吓<br />\n再者呢啲咁<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">和理非-學術活動</span></span><br />\n武力清場應該難以服眾<br />\n<br />\n請問有冇有經驗巴絲可以俾啲意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n#不割蓆<br />\n以下開放討論"},{"pid":"bd008017fd5f4e8aed96b96540e263b5f588e981","tid":1426995,"uid":70217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T04:40:35.000Z","msg":"朋友一番好意，希望大家一齊brainstorm 下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d67b9d59157150a8fb946dbc81feef2a2635b9a2","tid":1426995,"uid":70217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T04:48:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fae81ffde7e03ab84701f732c024690cf726